---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Indian Catering Vancouver | Wedding & Corporate Catering | Sula Since 2010"
	description="Award-winning Indian catering Vancouver since 2010. Wedding catering, corporate catering, samosa & finger food catering. Halal, vegan, vegetarian. From $21.95 per person."
	canonical="/"
>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/vancouver-catering-sula-indian-restaurant.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<p class="gold-label">Award-Winning Since 2010</p>
			<h1>The Art of <em>Indian Catering</em><br/>in Vancouver</h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">From intimate gatherings to grand weddings — flawlessly executed, exquisitely presented, and rooted in 15 years of craft.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/request-a-quote/" class="btn btn-gold">Begin Your Event</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">A Heritage of Hospitality</p>
				<h2>Vancouver's Most Trusted <em>Indian Catering</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p>For over fifteen years, we've been catering Vancouver's finest occasions — from intimate dinners to weddings of 500. Whether you're planning <a href="/weddings" class="inline-link">wedding catering in Vancouver</a>, an office lunch, or a Diwali celebration, our kitchen brings the same care to every plate. Our menus draw from North Indian, South Indian, Hyderabadi, and Goan traditions. House-ground spices. Halal-certified meats. And vegan, vegetarian, and gluten-friendly options on every menu.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp" alt="Indian food catering Vancouver Burnaby Richmond" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<!-- 2x2 SERVICE GRID -->
	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Our Catering Services · Since 2010</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Catering for Every <em>Occasion</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="service-grid-v2">
				<a href="/weddings" class="service-card-v2 reveal" aria-label="Wedding catering services">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/WEDDING.jpg" alt="Indian wedding catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Most Loved</span>
							<h3>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Sangeet, ceremony, reception. Custom menus crafted with our chefs. Halal, vegetarian, vegan, Jain.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Weddings →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-100" aria-label="Corporate catering services">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond-for-corporate-offices-private-parties-and-weddings.webp" alt="Corporate catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Trusted by Vancouver's Best</span>
							<h3>Corporate <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Boardroom lunches, conferences, client entertaining. Hot delivery, on time, every time.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Corporate →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-200" aria-label="Private party catering services">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-catering-vancouver-for-private-parties-birthdays-celebrations.webp" alt="Private party catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Birthdays & Milestones</span>
							<h3>Private <em>Parties</em></h3>
							<p>Birthdays, anniversaries, housewarmings, Diwali. Vibrant feasts, effortlessly delivered.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Private →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-300" aria-label="Café and chai catering services">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="https://sulacafe.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/sula-cafe-near-me-vancouver.webp" alt="Sula Cafe chai catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">From Sula Café</span>
							<h3>Café & <em>Chai</em></h3>
							<p>Live masala chai stations, specialty coffee bars, fresh-baked Indian pastries.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Café →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- THE EXPERIENCE -->
	<section class="section section-plum">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/weddinf-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Sula wedding catering Vancouver BC" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<p class="gold-label">The Sula Experience</p>
					<h2>Crafted with <em>Care.</em><br/>Served with <em>Soul.</em></h2>
					<p>Every menu begins with a conversation. We listen — to your story, your guests, your dreams for the day. Then we build something exclusively yours, drawing from the regional cuisines of India and the discipline of fifteen years catering Vancouver's finest occasions.</p>
					<p>Our <a href="/blog/halal-indian-catering-vancouver" class="inline-link">halal-certified meats</a> come from trusted local BC suppliers. Our pure-vegetarian and Jain dishes are prepared in dedicated kitchen areas. Vegan and gluten-free options are part of every menu — never an afterthought.</p>
					<div class="experience-stats">
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">15+</div><div class="stat-label">Years</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">2,000+</div><div class="stat-label">Events</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">4</div><div class="stat-label">Locations</div></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="image-banner" style="background-image: url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp');">
		<div class="image-banner-content reveal">
			<h2>Authentic Flavours, <em>Effortless Service</em></h2>
			<p>From boardroom to ballroom — we handle every detail.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container-narrow">
			<div class="reveal text-center">
				<p class="eyebrow">Our Philosophy</p>
				<div class="pull-quote">
					<p class="pull-quote-text">A great meal isn't just <em>tasted</em> — it's <em>remembered</em>. Every guest who walks away from a Sula table carries something with them: a flavour, a moment, a feeling of being truly cared for.</p>
					<p class="pull-quote-attribution">— The Sula Kitchen</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Recent Events</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Moments <em>Worth Celebrating</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;font-size:16px;color:rgba(26,26,26,0.75)">A glimpse from our <a href="/gallery" class="inline-link">full catering gallery</a> — real Vancouver weddings, corporate events, and celebrations.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="gallery-grid">
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-bc-canada.webp" alt="Indian food catering Vancouver BC" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-100"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/indian-catering-near-me-vancouver.webp" alt="Indian catering near me Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-200"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/office-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Office catering Vancouver BC" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-300"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/indian-catering-near-me-vancouver-birthdays-parties.webp" alt="Birthday party catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-top:60px">
				<a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-outline-dark">View Full Gallery</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="testimonial-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">A Word From Our Hosts</p>
				<p class="testimonial-quote">Sula didn't just cater our wedding — they made it unforgettable. Every guest still talks about the food, and our coordinator made the entire day effortless.</p>
				<p class="testimonial-author">— Priya & Arjun · Wedding for 350 Guests</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FROM THE JOURNAL -->
	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">From the Journal</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Catering <em>Insights & Guides</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="related-links">
				<a href="/blog/indian-wedding-catering-vancouver-guide" class="related-link reveal">
					<p class="meta">Wedding Planning · 8 min</p>
					<h4>Indian Wedding Catering: <em>The Complete Guide</em></h4>
					<p>Sangeet menus, halal certification, dietary planning, and everything we wish every couple knew before booking.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Read the Guide →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/blog/office-catering-vancouver-large-groups" class="related-link reveal delay-100">
					<p class="meta">Corporate Catering · 6 min</p>
					<h4>Office Catering: <em>Feeding 50+ at Work</em></h4>
					<p>Practical guidance on planning a large office lunch — guest count, dietary needs, delivery timing.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Read More →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/blog/halal-indian-catering-vancouver" class="related-link reveal delay-200">
					<p class="meta">Catering Essentials · 5 min</p>
					<h4>Halal Indian <em>Catering</em></h4>
					<p>What halal certification means, how to ask the right questions, and why it matters for multi-cultural events.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Read More →</span>
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-top:60px">
				<a href="/blog" class="btn btn-outline-dark">View All Articles</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<p class="gold-label" style="color:var(--gold-light)">Begin the Conversation</p>
			<h2>Let's Plan Something <em>Extraordinary</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us about your event. We'll respond within 24 hours with a custom menu and quote.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/request-a-quote/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
